rComments: The worst class I have taken in 3 years while at U of I.  Each class there is a quiz or a group exercise which she grades very tough and the only grades in the class except for a cumulative final.  She is very poor at explaining simple concepts and I would rather watch paint dry than try and listen to one of her lectures. Do not take this.
Horrible did not explain things well at all. If for a gen-ed I would not recommend it. Especially because there is only two exams and it is confusing how she teaches so thumbs down.
